text: Ryan Whitney Newman (born April 24, 1998) is an American actress. She is best known for her roles as Ginger Falcone in Disney XD's Zeke and Luther, Allison in The Thundermans, Cindy Collins in Zoom and Emily Hobbs in See Dad Run. In 2015, Whitney played Claudia Shepard in Sharknado 3: Oh Hell No!. In 2024, she played Margaret "Mugs" Cleaver in the biopic Reagan. Whitney was born in 1998.
